text: Josette Nevière (born 8 April 1933) is a French alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:French female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of France Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:People from Thonon-les-Bains Category:Sportspeople from Haute-Savoie
